// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0625 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a6d13eba-9c40-5011-a948-5f4a1fde56d8

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
